title: Fishing rod
description: A fishing rod is a long, flexible tool used in fishing to cast a fishing line, control the bait or lure, and catch fish. It works by bending under tension, helping anglers feel bites and reel in fish smoothly.

title: oven
description: An oven is a kitchen appliance used for cooking, baking, roasting, and heating food by surrounding it with controlled heat. It is commonly used to prepare foods like cakes, bread, pizza, cookies, roasted vegetables, and meats.

title: Speakers
description: Speakers are electronic audio output devices that convert electrical audio signals into sound waves, allowing us to hear music, speech, and other audio clearly. They are used in homes, vehicles, computers, mobile devices, and public sound systems.
